Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, more to the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, it's called a "camera."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever I see shows up in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, I bought this when I went to a foreigner's mansion just the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the ship docked, lots of things have come into the city of Edo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll take a picture. Stand still, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you shouldn't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Magoroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, someone's getting in our way to this extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person's eye seemed wretched...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like someone full of bitterness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bitterness," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unfortunate, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our duty as assassins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karyuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that creature appears again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi-sama, it's Magoroku-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The men of Daikokuya Rihei,\N the ones dealing in dry goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't question the means you employ, as long as they're brought down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Magoroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,speaking of the Rihei, weren't they your intimate friends long ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they mustn't be allowed to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, betrayal cannot be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Betrayal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bastards, stealing my business...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:05:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops! Please, don't ask any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First things first: here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you accept it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, if it isn't Karyuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You displayed excellent skills back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friendship you and I share, Karyuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magoroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't touch Karyuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one who's slept with Karyuu has come out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'm depending on you, Daikokuya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring them down as soon as you can, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured, and leave it all to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be any mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, people like you would do anything for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fearsome man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such jokes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kourin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an intruder down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You let him get away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's light on his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act so calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go after him already, and be sure to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magoroku is Rihei's business competitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Miss. We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, she's alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she with Rihei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is that girl planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like Daikokuya, to be so thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fewer merchants nowadays display such courtesy, and it troubles me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still a virgin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have fine skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been spotted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him! Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kourin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you've realized it now, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The poison should take effect quite soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop resisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, you're a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So unfortunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you feel good before you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enchanting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait. I'll give you pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, time to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That... dream again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Gisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drinking this will give you a little relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've drawn out the poison, but not the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a foolish man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he'd finished you off right then,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything would've been over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take off the bandages now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, what's this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my home. You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gisuke-dono, was it? You've taken care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better for you not to move yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. In time, my pursuers will come to your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remain here, I'll only cause you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a temporary home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably meet you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost like a nymph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such skin... I've never seen its like before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From heaven... or from hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter which.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to work more and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? Would you like a sip?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Western wine is hard to get a hold of, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that shouldn't be wasted on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how are Rihei's defenses?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being, I believe it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, Tokugawa's night will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magoroku, beware the shogunate's dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.75,0:21:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uzume, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that I won't allow you to move about on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wash me, Gisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:17.15,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(Note: This chant is an exorcism against spirits consumed by demons.)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin, pyou, tou, sha, kai, jin, retsu, zai... zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll place my stone here. How about {\i1}that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:26.36,DefaultIllM,,0000,0000,0000,,You're placing too many stones with no strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:26.80,Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are enough stones...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:22:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rihei's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems your wounds have totally healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an assassin, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to get in my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.08,0:24:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.79,0:24:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Treasure your life."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.71,0:24:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karyuu, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.75,0:24:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get involved in this business.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.97,0:24:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't kill Rihei yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.26,0:25:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though Magoroku paid you to do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.64,0:25:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.27,0:25:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not trust Magoroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.19,0:25:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world will change,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.65,0:25:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you won't even realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.53,0:25:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, an assassin like you will be needed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.12,0:25:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blood of a true assassin flows in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.41,0:25:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and so, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.59,0:25:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.13,0:25:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will only follow my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.48,0:25:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.18,0:25:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karyuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.48,0:25:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinoto! Stay there!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.44,0:25:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all, Karyuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.98,0:25:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your real enemy is somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.49,0:25:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.32,0:25:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.70,0:26:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.31,0:26:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rihei...
